00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,500
Scenes & Navigation Scenes let you jump to
named checkpoints without navigating slide
by slide. Keyboard shortcuts: - `Ctrl+G` /
`Cmd+G` — open the slide picker -
`Alt+Left` — go back to the previous slide
- Type a slide number + `Enter` — jump
directly

